## Mirrors

Issues and pull requests are accepted on both GitHub and Codeberg, although CI and releases are only on github.

- GitHub: https://github.com/Oppzippy/OpenSCQ30
- Codeberg: https://codeberg.org/Oppzippy/OpenSCQ30

